          "timestamp": "2024-04-08T08:19:45Z",
          "message_type": "建议",
          "emotional_tone": "积极"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "patient",
          "message": "明白了，我这就去菜市场买点新鲜的。谢谢医生！",
